  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n                <i>You have mastered a small handful of spells, and can prepare these spells without referencing your spellbooks at all.</i>\n                <br />\n                <br />\n                \n                <p><b>Prerequisites</b></p>\n                <p> 1st-level wizard</p>\n                \n            <br />\n                <p><b>Benefits</b></p>\n                <p><p class=\"stat-block-1\"> Each time you take this feat, choose a number of spells that you already know equal to your Intelligence modifier. From that point on, you can prepare these spells without referring to a spellbook.</p></p>\n                \n            <br />\n                <p><b>Normal</b></p>\n                <p><p class=\"stat-block-1\"> Without this feat, you must use a spellbook to prepare all your spells, except <i>read magic</i>.</p></p>\n                \n            \n            "
